  <brief_title>A Study of Solifenacin With Bladder Training Versus Solifenacin Alone in Patients With Overactive Bladder (SOLAR)</brief_title>
  <acronym>SOLAR</acronym>
  <official_title>Solifenacin Succinate in a Flexible Dose Regimen With Simplified Bladder Training Versus Solifenacin Succinate in a Flexible Dose Regimen Alone in a Prospective, Randomized, Parallel Group, Overactive Bladder Symptom Study</official_title>
